
# Messenger

## Setup

```
mkdir messenger && cd messenger
curl -L https://github.com/electron/electron/releases/download/v1.8.4/electron-v1.8.4-linux-x64.zip -o tmp.zip
unzip tmp.zip
rm tmp.zip
mkdir resources/app
curl -L http://github.com/adabru/messenger/archive/master.tar.gz | tar xz -C resources/app --strip 1

# start it
./electron
```
